track_notes:
Rote from Storey Inn CP.
Steep towards the top. No real tracks lower down but well defined towards the top.

Total time (including ops): 4hr 30m. Maximum difficulty: Swiss Alpine Club Grade T1. Uncurated GPX which may contain navigation errors, detours and hazards. Additional route information may be available at www.m1hax.uk. Track data by Richard M1HAX licensed under Creative Commons BY-NC-SA.
track_title: Fan Fawr Circuit from A470. Nov 2018.

track_notes: There is ample parking in the designated off road parking.  The path follows the main track to towards the reservoir to the gate.  After the gate an indestinct track leads off sharp left through the undergrowth.  The bush wacking can be avoided by walking a short distance up the road to the cattle grid and walking accross the open field to join the path. From here there is a steady ascent on a reasonable path all the way to the summit.
